# Isabella Photography

Isabella Photography comes with an incredible creative design and 6 months of support included. It is designed for people with basic knowledge in web development where we use simply HTML, CSS and JAVASCRIPT or we have a more advanced alternative where we use PUG, STYLUS, GULP among other things.

## Installation Advanced Developers

To use this template, your computer needs:

- [NodeJS](https://nodejs.org/en/) (0.12 or greater)
- [Git](https://git-scm.com/)
- [PUG](https://pugjs.org/)

### Manual Setup

Then open the folder app in your command line, and install the needed dependencies:

```bash
cd app
npm install
```

Finally type the name of the `gulp` task in the console to compile Stylus + PUG and execute all the tasks created in the gulpfile.js